title: Randi Rhodes Show with Nicole Sandler - October 09 2013
description:
October 09, 2013
The Randi Rhodes Show with Nicole Sandler

Randi's out today, but will be back tomorrow. Nicole Sandler's sitting in today with the latest news and some great guests too...

With the shutdown dragging on and the debt ceiling default looming, Americans want to know what will happen if the tea freak Republicans do push the nation over the edge. Forbes columnist Rick Ungar will join Nicole to discuss the cartoonish Republicans, the actual consequences of a U.S. default, and the one thing Republicans may have right about Obamacare.

Josh Eidelson of Salon will cover the neo-Confederate rage behind the shutdown, where the filibuster fits into the debt ceiling stand-off, and how Dems may be falling into a Tea Party language trap.
